FAQ_TITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Cat Image UI
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Find answers to common questions about our user interface for browsing and sharing cat pictures.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How do I upload my cat photos?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Just click the 'Upload' button, select the images from your device, and our app will upload and display your cute cat pics!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Can I share my favorite cat images?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Absolutely! Every image has a 'Share' option that lets you easily share the adorable cat photo on social media or via messaging apps.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How can I search for specific cat breeds or colors?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Use the search bar at the top to filter images based on breed, color, or other keywords. Our smart filtering helps you find exactly the type of cat you want to see!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is there a way to save my favorite cat pics?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, just click the heart icon on any image to add it to your 'Favorites' collection. You can access your saved favorites anytime.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How often is new cat content added?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Our cat-loving community is constantly uploading new adorable feline photos and videos every day. The latest uploads are featured on the home page.

PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Cat Image UI
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What types of cat images can I upload?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our UI accepts JPG, PNG, and GIF image formats for all types of cat pictures - from kittens to senior cats, household pets to big cats.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How do I upload cat images?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Simply click the 'Upload Image' button, select the cat photo(s) you want to upload from your device, and our UI will display them instantly.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I add captions or descriptions to the images?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, after uploading images you can add custom captions describing the cats, their names, breeds, etc. Just click on the caption field below each image.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How can I share or save the uploaded cat images?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: You can easily share individual images or your whole uploaded gallery via social media or email using the share buttons. To save images, just right-click and choose 'Save Image As'.
